<div class="add-padding-top help-text">
    <h2 class="add-padding-bottom-5">
        Manage Transaction
    </h2>
    <p>
        When a registrant pays via their credit card, that creates a credit card request. For each request, you can process multiple refunds up to the amount of the original refund. You cannot process and additional payment on this request. You have to start a new request from the <b>Manage Registration</b> view.
    </p>
    <p>
        For more information on billing and transaction management, <a class="text-color-2" href="~/Help/Billing" target="_blank">click here</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
        Click <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign text-color-1"></span> below for more details.
    </p>
</div>

